f740.value:






Basis of preparation

    The Consolidated financial statements are:



        prepared in accordance with International Financial Reporting Standards (IFRS)
        as adopted by the European Union (EU) and comply with the statutory provisions
        of Part 9, Book 2 of the Dutch Civil Code;


        authorized for issue by the Board of Management of Royal Philips on February 21,
        2023;


        prepared under the historical cost convention, unless otherwise indicated;


        prepared on a going concern basis;


        presented in euro, which is the presentation currency;


        rounded to the nearest million euro unless stated otherwise;


        subject to rounding, whereby amounts may not add up precisely to the totals
        provided.

